OL,4,CCovid: Cardiff ice rink to reopen after
OL,5,C'frustrating' wait
OL,6, One of Wales' two ice rinks is set to
OL,7, reopen on Monday, almost 17 months
OL,8, after closing its doors.
OL,10,FThe Welsh government gave the go-ahead
OL,11,Ffor ice rinks to reopen on 17 July, but
OL,12,Fwork to prepare Ice Arena Wales in
OL,13,FCardiff Bay had not been finished.
OL,15,FWales' other rink, the Deeside Leisure
OL,16,FCentre, remains closed while it is used
OL,17,Fas a mass Covid vaccination centre.
OL,19,FIce rinks were one of the final sectors
OL,20,Fto be allowed to reopen, with the Welsh
OL,21,Fgovernment citing high infection risks.
